# Data Pipeline Design

## Medallion Data Architecture for Real-Time Ecommerce Analytics

---

# 1. Overview

The data platform in this project follows the **Medallion Architecture**, a design pattern widely used in modern data platforms built on Delta Lake and Databricks.

The Medallion pattern organizes data into progressively refined layers:

| Layer | Purpose |
|------|--------|
| Bronze | Raw ingested data |
| Silver | Cleaned and enriched data |
| Gold | Business-ready datasets |

This layered approach ensures **data reliability, reproducibility, and scalability**.

